# Alerts


If you want to use alerts first you need to add the mars-alert style and classe to a css element. To do this you should add the mars-alert builder like:

<% example_tabs do %>

<% example_html do %>
<div class="alert">
  JPEG, PNG, GIF or BMP - 5MB file limit, at least 250x250 pixels.
</div>
<% end %>

~~~scss
.alert { @include mars-alert; }
~~~

~~~css
.alert {
  /* ///////// üõ∏ mars-alert */
  padding: 1.5rem;
  color: #f9b13d;
  background-color: rgba(249, 177, 61, 0.04);
  border: 1px solid;
  border-radius: 3px;
  margin-top: 0;
  margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .alert.is-dismissible {
    position: relative;
    padding-right: 3rem; }
  .alert a {
    color: inherit;
    border-bottom: 1px solid; }
    .alert a:hover {
      color: inherit; }
~~~
<% end %>


